title: The 5 Things We're All Facing Right Now with Lysa Terkeurst, John Mark Comer, Jada Edwards, Bianca Olthoff, and Shelley Giglio
description:
Bitterness, busyness, feeling small, fear, weariness. We are in a new season, a new world and we need to know how to move forward from here. From these hard places. This is just a taste of a one-day gathering called IF:Lead and I want you to be there with me.

Use code JENNIE10 for $10 off an individual pass here IFLEAD2021.com
